
---

## `.gitignore`

```gitignore
# ---- Python ----
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*.pyd
*.pyo
*.pkl
*.log
*.sqlite3

# ---- Virtual environments ----
venv/
.venv/
env/
ENV/

# ---- Packaging / build ----
build/
dist/
*.egg-info/
.eggs/

# ---- Test / coverage ----
.pytest_cache/
.coverage
htmlcov/
coverage.xml

# ---- IDE / editors ----
.vscode/
.idea/
*.iml

# ---- OS ----
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# ---- Env / secrets ----
.env
*.pem
*.key
*.crt

# ---- Audio / media artifacts ----
*.wav
*.mp3
*.m4a
*.ogg
*.flac


# ---- Jupyter ----
.ipynb_checkpoints/
